questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to provide you to get started with a design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
1. Logo Design/Color scheme 
2. Text Content/copy (if you already have it)
3. Wireframes/Rough sketch (if you have any)
4. Brief description of the Business
5. Inspirational/Competitor's website

questionsAndAnswers.question: I don't have a Logo/Color Scheme. Can you design a logo for me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will design 5 outstanding Logos for your business. From which you can select the best match for the website. Here is my Logo Design Gig https://www.fiverr.com/share/eYX7Rk

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is a Fiverr PRO seller?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: A seller who meets the Fiverr Pro standards will have a Pro badge added to their profile. Every Pro Gig is labeled with a Pro badge so that buyers know they're getting the very best.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What I will receive as source files?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
For the Basic gig (Design Only): Figma/Adobe XD source file
For Standard and Premium Package : Figma/Adobe XD + HTML CSS/ReactJS Source Files

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide coding services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, my standard and Premium package includes coding.
